summary:
Mates, please calm down
He said he’s “hoping” to “perhaps” upload in June.
Please, please don’t get the idea that he is...
body:
Mates, please calm down

He said he’s “hoping” to “perhaps” upload in June.

Please, please don’t get the idea that he is definitely uploading!!! Otherwise we run into the same problems we have had in the past, when he regrets telling us anything because we spin his words into something he didn’t say and then we get angry when he doesn’t do what he said he wouldn’t do!!

I am just as excited that he is planning to come back, but give him some space to breathe. If he doesn’t end up uploading, please be kind and understanding. He didn’t guarantee it. He just said he would try. So treat it that way, okay?

summary: Whenever I start thinking about caterpillars, I start having a mild crisis— bear with me. Because, they start as caterpillars,...
body: Whenever I start thinking about caterpillars, I start having a mild crisis— bear with me. Because, they start as caterpillars, they have a lovely time munching on all the leaves, everything’s great. Then, they turn into a cocoon, w- like, what is happening? But THEN, they don’t just grow wings! If you actually watch a video about this, they turn into a full on mush— like a caterpillar soup— before they, then, REFORM into a butterfly. Like, what the HELL is going on? What does that MEAN? Imagine if a human, from a baby, just turned into a weird mush and then just popped out as an adult that could fly around. And not only that, they only live for, like, a day as a butterfly, so what’s the POINT in turning into that soup for all that time, if you’re just gonna live for a day and fly around? Why don’t they just stay as a caterpillar, eating all the food? I just wanna stay as a caterpillar! I CAN’T HANDLE IT ANYMORE.

summary: I don't want to hear A THING about how Dan "will postpone the video" even longer than June. And what if he does? He gave us a...
body:
I don’t want to hear A THING about how Dan “will postpone the video” even longer than June. And what if he does? He gave us a month to have at least some hope to get a vid in and he wasn’t obligated to do that. He’s on an indefinite time break, and I’m tired of “I respect this, BUT…”. No.

Here, come at me, I’ve got enough. I’ve already seen comments on a one post on Instagram, almost all of them full of this negativity. Don’t do that. I am excited, I got so exited when I saw that reply. Don’t riun it for me, for others, just because you have catastrophic thoughts. I am a pessimist, a strong one, but I got fucking excited because he really is thinking of coming back, or at least so it seems, and I’m NOT gonna fall to those who are there to just ruin the excitement.

Thank you, I’ll pass.
